{"tid":124240,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"呢度有冇巴打當年追過海貓鳴泣之時遊戲?","createTime":"2017-02-17T12:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T07:13:04.000Z","uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f4ae80f069be031c810f21ed3a54ff63539a45e","tid":124240,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T12:34:18.000Z","msg":"當年一路追一路估真相真係幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n網上有好多高手EP1～4已經估中左大部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（紗嘉一體，白馬之約，EP1~3全手法等等）<br />\n之後隔左一排，聽到EP5新OP，又係勁感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEP7好好睇，雖然死都唔拆貓箱整走好多Fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1baff22c256b463ba57b5d0dfaf54e05e1cafe10","tid":124240,"uid":24592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T13:03:22.000Z","msg":"佢漫畫版好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ngame本身毀左龍騎士07個招牌"},{"pid":"a8f29aed93cc5cb126ee2ea7e94757d4cb34785d","tid":124240,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T13:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢漫畫版好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ngame本身毀左龍騎士07個招牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n漫畫個尾完得唔錯，配埋依兩首BGM真係幾感動<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2SzP8etu6HY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2SzP8etu6HY&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f740fda5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2SzP8etu6HY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CWSE7r7vo6c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCWSE7r7vo6c&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=1fbb3145\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CWSE7r7vo6c</a>"},{"p