kquote><br />\n同我差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年網上D高手真係痴線，紗嘉一體說真係講中左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e186b7b9591f17a471307416214629a5493faf7e","tid":124240,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只係睇漫畫簡直係人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早兩日終於睇完漫畫<br />\n漫畫挑得太明，有D無癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2323d6c591abb480f17c3ef36f148075a6b561c","tid":124240,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"淨係記得當年睇晒動畫 覺得極度無離頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近補完漫畫 先覺得套野唔錯"},{"pid":"7b63e3d28a9333d32baa39be97a33478bc342242","tid":124240,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:54:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>只係睇漫畫簡直係人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左ep8龍騎太乞人憎之外 其他ep我覺得都係game好啲<br />\n龍騎寫推理9流 但劇情係高質<br />\n同埋劇情以外 最重要係音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且當年真係會抄低紅字推理<br />\n當時追完一個ep 再上大陸壇睇前原K1推理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEp8 game 同漫畫劇情係咪有唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b8e5886ff08e76e45a198f072acd5b324187b2","tid":124240,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>只係睇漫畫簡直係人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左ep8龍騎太乞人憎之外 其他ep我覺得都係game好啲<br />\n龍騎寫推理9流 但劇情係高質<br />\n同埋劇情以外 最重要係音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且當年真係會抄低紅字推理<br />\n當時追完一個ep 再上大陸壇睇前原K1推理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEp8 game 同漫畫劇情係咪有唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n漫畫有加料，解返多D野，但如果有心睇，去到EP7已經明晒<br />\nEP8問題係係度串讀者，指責讀者揭開貓箱"},{"pid":"6ba1d4487098c091f95787f408b357eef135ed32","tid":124240,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T19:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>只係睇漫畫簡直係人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左ep8龍騎太乞人憎之外 其他ep我覺得都係game好啲<br />\n龍騎寫推理9流 但劇情係高質<br />\n同埋劇情以外 最重要係音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且當年真係會抄低紅字推理<br />\n當時追完一個ep 再上大陸壇睇前原K1推理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEp8 game 同漫畫劇情係咪有唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n漫畫有加料，解返多D野，但如果有心睇，去到EP7已經明晒<br />\nEP8問題係係度串讀者，指責讀者揭開貓箱</blockquote><br />\n其實ep7已經發晦氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真相就係次男夫婦殺全家 比繪羽反殺 <br />\n之後一直做醜人呃緣壽<br />\n明明比曬真相 但係發晦氣咁比答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd6a5b65e805c62f9bec11b14237a5d6f8fb26f","tid":124240,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T19:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打當年有追?<br />\n好多人都係睇漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我追game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEp4開始逐個ep等漢化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk